[[!template id=infobox_person name="Roger Ver" names="Bitcoin Jesus" bitcointalk="[https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?action=profile;u=10310 10310]"]]**Roger Ver**, sometimes dubbed **Bitcoin Jesus**, is the founder and CEO of [MemoryDealers](https://memorydealers.com/), and a Bitcoin evangelist.

[[!img "memorydealers_roadsign.jpg" size=120x120 title="A June 2011 billboard promoting Bitcoin paid for by Roger Ver"]]

He is one of [[BitPay]]'s investors, and was involved/invested with [[BlockChain.info]]/MyWallet as well.

In 2002 Ver plead guilty to selling explosives on eBay. (1.1)
